reviews.text: Office building that houses a lot of financial firms and is well connected to other key finance buildings in central Hong Kong. Great food court at the bottom floor, with adjacent greenery areas and an overall great reception area. Not the best communications as getting down to the MTR or the main tram line can be a bit of a hassle, but the views are worth it for the higher floors.
Great spot cause I work here. Simply life is great.
They do offer classical music performance every Friday after office hour.  Very thoughtful indeed.
Good place for Saturday breakfast
